the future of” is a bit of an exaggeration, but... actually, I'm thinking of having a sakura party hosted by RiNG.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event253-01-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Wow~! It's kind of unusual to have a sakura party hosted by a studio, isn't it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"Ririko","body":"There are still some bands around here who have never used RiNG's studio, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event253-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"Ririko","body":"Through this event, we hope that this sakura party will be a good opportunity for them to know about and use RiNG.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event253-01-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":40}],"windowDisplayName":"Taki","body":"The fact that RiNG is hosting this event means that I have to help out as a staff member, right? This is the first time I'm hearing about this.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":40,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":40,"voiceId":"event253-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"Ririko","body":"We finally came to an agreement the other day, and I was just about to tell everyone about it today~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event253-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Don't sulk, Rikki.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile04","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Sorry, Taki-chan. Kasumi and I were asked to talk to band girls who might be interested in joining us, so we found out slightly earlier.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event253-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":40}],"windowDisplayName":"Taki","body":"I'm not sulking... That's enough.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":40,"motionName":"sigh01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":40,"voiceId":"event253-01-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Hey, hey, Taki-chan, Anon-chan. Would MyGO!!!!! like to join the sakura party?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Oh~, I appreciate you inviting us, but I feel that for MyGO!!!!!, RiNG is already our home...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"Ririko","body":"Oh, Taki-chan, you can join in with the band members as usual. I'm going to ask Kasumi-chan and Saya-chan to organize the bands that have joined the event, and have them enjoy the sakura party afterwards.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event253-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Let's do the sakura party~! It will definitely be fun!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"I'm calling on various bands right now. It's going to be pretty lively.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event253-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Are they bands that we know?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Yeah, probably.  Among the bands that have played with MyGO!!!!! before, Afterglow is one we've gotten a response from already.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event253-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":40}],"windowDisplayName":"Taki","body":"Afterglow-san...!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":40,"motionName":"surprised02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":40,"voiceId":"event253-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Also, I just got replies from Morfonica, Hello, Happy World! and Pastel*Palettes! Roselia and RAISE A SUILEN will come if they finish their errands early!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"Saya","body":"Kasumi, that's why you were so excited just now.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"ando01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event253-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"That's right!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event253-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Except for Afterglow, maybe I don't know much about the other bands. Morfonica, Hello, Happy World! and Paspare...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":37,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":37}],"windowDisplayName":"Anon","body":"Huh? By Paspare, do you mean Pastel*Palettes?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":37,"voiceId":"event253-01-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"Kasumi","body":"Yeah, that's the idol band Pastel*Palettes!","tenti